name: Iconoir -- The Definitive Open Source Icons Library
description:
Iconoir is one of the biggest open source libraries with currently 914 SVG Icons. No premium icons, no email sign-up, no newsletters.


  • All icons are converted to a component
  • Organized into groups, convenient to use as a team library


https://iconoir.com/

914 Icons // SVG, Font, React // MIT License
